{"tid":2219451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"解放軍震懾台灣齊發10枚東風導彈 網揭是假的","createTime":"2020-09-27T01:18:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T01:22:23.000Z","uid":294518,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"95990271c5e75c3a4b486bf037aa1ca6ad5f8157","tid":2219451,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T01:18:17.000Z","msg":"解放軍震懾台灣齊發10枚東風導彈 網揭是假的<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20200926-%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8D%E9%9C%87%E6%87%BE%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E9%BD%8A%E7%99%BC10%E6%9E%9A%E6%9D%B1%E9%A2%A8%E5%B0%8E%E5%BD%88-%E7%B6%B2%E6%8F%AD%E6%98%AF%E5%81%87%E7%9A%84\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F20200926-%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%2594%25BE%25E8%25BB%258D%25E9%259C%2587%25E6%2587%25BE%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E9%25BD%258A%25E7%2599%25BC10%25E6%259E%259A%25E6%259D%25B1%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E5%25B0%258E%25E5%25BD%2588-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%258F%25AD%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%2581%2587%25E7%259A%2584&d=31jm0GaxjznMjcF0xOQh0nO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=d655f4ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20200926-%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8D%E9%9C%87%E6%87%BE%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E9%BD%8A%E7%99%BC10%E6%9E%9A%E6%9D%B1%E9%A2%A8%E5%B0%8E%E5%BD%88-%E7%B6%B2%E6%8F%AD%E6%98%AF%E5%81%87%E7%9A%84</a><br />\n<br />\n中國軍媒周四（24日）發布一段10枚東風-11A導彈連發的影片，稱東部戰區火箭軍一導彈旅近日進行實彈演習，成功摧毀目標機堡、跑道，其對台震懾意味甚濃。港媒稱，但有眼利網民發現部分片段與4年前解放軍在戈壁沙漠試射導彈後釋出的畫面雷同，亦有畫面疑取自電視劇，令人質疑解放軍的影片只是剪接而成。<br />\n<br />\n報道指但有網民發現，影片與官媒於2016年12月發布的&ldquo;2016大演兵&rdquo;內的畫面相同，包括導彈連射，及射中目標物後爆破等。另外片段一開始為軍隊從山區基地出發，後突然變成多輛軍車在戈壁荒漠中奔馳，剪接痕跡明顯。而10彈齊射的場景，更與電視劇《號手就位》的預告片畫面相似，只是色調不一樣。"},{"pid":"68783b65cb9e22fa68a8d7e3bf49174f205d8f3f","tid":2219451,"uid":4942,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T01:19:23.000Z","msg":"做假大國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95a7eafb154123b7ca26daa965234160554519d9","tid":2219451,"uid":297997,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T01:20:25.000Z","msg":"假係一回事<br />\n<br />\n有冇咁多粒東風，就算有，捨唔捨得咁用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bbfa9de7fc237ed07677c214997a6611908fed2","tid":2219451,"uid":57677,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T01:22:23.000Z","msg":"台灣天弓係真㗎喎"}]}